olute inset-0\"><img alt=\"Mendocino coastline\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover opacity-20\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fmendocino-coast.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fmendocino-coast.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fmendocino-coast.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fmendocino-coast.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fmendocino-coast.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fmendocino-coast.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fmendocino-coast.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fmendocino-coast.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fmendocino-coast.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-dem-blue via-dem-blue/95 to-dem-blue-dark/90\"></div></div><div class=\"relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><h1 class=\"text-4xl font-extrabold text-white sm:text-5xl\">Chartered Clubs</h1><p class=\"mt-4 text-xl text-white/80\">Democratic clubs serving communities across Mendocino County</p></div></section><section class=\"py-16 sm:py-20\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><p class=\"mb-12 max-w-3xl text-lg text-dem-gray-600\">Mendocino County is home to several chartered Democratic clubs, each serving different regions of our county. Clubs are a great way to meet fellow Democrats, stay informed on local issues, and get involved in your community.</p><div class=\"grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-dem-gray-200 bg-white shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg\"><div class=\"flex h-40 w-full items-center justify-center bg-white px-8 py-6\"><img alt=\"Mendocino Coast Democratic Club\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"280\" height=\"120\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"h-auto max-h-28 w-auto max-w-full object-contain\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcoast-club.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcoast-club.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcoast-club.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75\"/></div><div class=\"border-b border-dem-gray-200 bg-dem-gray-50 p-6\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-dem-gray-900\">Mendocino Coast Democratic Club</h2><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm font-medium text-dem-blue\">Fort Bragg / Mendocino Coast</p></div><div class=\"p-6\"><div class=\"prose prose-sm max-w-none\"><p>The Mendocino Coast Democratic Club serves Democrats along the beautiful Mendocino Coast, including Fort Bragg, Mendocino, and surrounding communities. The club hosts regular meetings, candidate forums, and community events.</p>\n</div><p class=\"mt-4 text-sm text-dem-gray-600\"><span class=\"font-semibold\">Meetings:</span> <!-- -->Monthly meetings</p><a href=\"https://www.coastdemocraticclub.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"mt-3 inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm font-semibold text-dem-blue hover:text-dem-blue-light\">Visit Website<svg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M13.5 6H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 003 8.25v10.5A2.25 2.25 0 005.25 21h10.5A2.25 2.25 0 0018 18.75V10.5m-10.5 6L21 3m0 0h-5.25M21 3v5.25\"></path></svg></a></div></div><div class=\"overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-dem-gray-200 bg-white shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg\"><div class=\"flex h-40 w-full items-center justify-center bg-white px-8 py-6\"><img alt=\"Inland Mendocino Democratic Club\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"280\" height=\"120\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"h-auto max-h-28 w-auto max-w-full object-contain\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Finland-club.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Finland-club.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Finland-club.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75\"/></div><div class=\"border-b border-dem-gray-200 bg-dem-gray-50 p-6\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-dem-gray-900\">Inland Mendocino Democratic Club</h2><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm font-medium text-dem-blue\">Ukiah / Inland Mendocino</p></div><div class=\"p-6\"><div class=\"prose prose-sm max-w-none\"><p>The Inland Mendocino Democratic Club serves the inland communities of Mendocino County, including Ukiah, Willits, and surrounding areas. The club is active in voter outreach, candidate support, and community organizing.</p>\n</div><p class=\"mt-4 text-sm text-dem-gray-600\"><span class=\"font-semibold\">Meetings:</span> <!-- -->Monthly meetings</p><a href=\"https://inlandmendodems.org/WP/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"mt-3 inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm font-semibold text-dem-blue hover:text-dem-blue-light\">Visit Website<svg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M13.5 6H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 003 8.25v10.5A2.25 2.25 0 005.25 21h10.5A2.25 2.25 0 0018 18.75V10.5m-10.5 6L21 3m0 0h-5.25M21 3v5.25\"></path></svg></a></div></div><div class=\"overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-dem-gray-200 bg-white shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg\"><div class=\"border-b border-dem-gray-200 bg-dem-gray-50 p-6\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-dem-gray-900\">Anderson Valley Democratic Club</h2><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm font-medium text-dem-blue\">Anderson Valley</p></div><div class=\"p-6\"><div class=\"prose prose-sm max-w-none\"><p>The Anderson Valley Democratic Club serves Democrats in the Anderson Valley area, including Boonville, Philo, and Navarro. The club brings together community members to discuss issues and support Democratic values in this unique and vibrant part of Mendocino County.</p>\n</div><p class=\"mt-4 text-sm text-dem-gray-600\"><span class=\"font-semibold\">Meetings:</span> <!-- -->Monthly meetings</p></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-12 rounded-xl bg-dem-blue/5 p-8 text-center\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-dem-blue\">Interested in Starting a Club?</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-dem-gray-600\">If there isn&#x27;t a Democratic club in your area and you&#x27;d like to start one, contact the Central Committee for information about the chartering process.</p><a href=\"/contact\" class=\"mt-6 inline-flex items-center rounded-lg bg-dem-blue px-6 py-3 font-semibold text-white transition-colors hover:bg-dem-blue-light\">Contact Us</a></div></div></section><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"bg-dem-blue-dark text-white\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:py-16\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4\"><div class=\"lg:col-span-2\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-white\">Mendocino County Democratic Central Committee</h2><address class=\"mt-4 not-italic leading-relaxed text-white/70\"><p>PO Box 28</p><p>Ukiah, CA 95482</p></address><div class=\"mt-6 flex items-center gap-4\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Mendodems/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white/10 p-2.5 text-white transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-white/20\" aria-label=\"Follow us on Facebook\"><svg class=\"h-5 w-5\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M22 12c0-5.523-4.477-10-10-10S2 6.477 2 12c0 4.991 3.657 9.128 8.438 9.878v-6.987h-2.54V12h2.54V9.797c0-2.506 1.492-3.89 3.777-3.89 1.094 0 2.238.195 2.238.195v2.46h-1.26c-1.243 0-1.63.771-1.63 1.562V12h2.773l-.443 2.89h-2.33v6.988C18.343 21.128 22 16.991 22 12z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://cadem.org/\" 